    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies how to use the cSHAKE hash for ORCHID
   generation and allows for varying sized hashes in the ORCHID along
   with additional information within the ORCHID.  It is an addendum to
   ORCHIDv2 [RFC7343].</t>
    </abstract>
